<html><body><p>On Saturday 17th November, <a title="Fierce Valley on Facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/FierceValleyRG" target="_blank">Fierce Valley Roller Girls</a>' Parma Violents will play host to <a title="Wirral Whipiteres on Facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Wirral-Whipiteres-Roller-Derby-Team/241886595869147?fref=ts" target="_blank">Wirral Whipiteres Roller Derby</a> in For Whom the Skate Rolls!

